    <item>
      <title>Kokkos training</title>
      <link>https://cexa-project.org/news/2023-07-27-kokkos-training/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://cexa-project.org/news/2023-07-27-kokkos-training/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;CExA organises a 3-days Kokkos training from the 20 to the 22 of Septembre in
Saclay provided by Kokkos lead developers
&lt;a href=&#34;https://extremecomputingtraining.anl.gov/speakers/christian-trott-snl/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Cristian Trott&lt;/a&gt;
and
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ornl.gov/staff-profile/damien-t-lebrun-grandie&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Damien Lebrun-Grandié&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Registration to the first day is free and open to all, but mandatory to attend:
&lt;a href=&#34;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/e/kokkos-1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/e/kokkos-1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following two days will consist in practical work in the lab room and
registration is limited to 30 people, with priority given to CEA members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where&lt;/strong&gt;: Neurospin Amphitheatre for day 1 and Maison de la Simulation for days
2 and 3.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When&lt;/strong&gt;: 20-22 of Septembre 2023.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://indico.math.cnrs.fr/e/kokkos-1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;register here!&lt;/a&gt; for day 1.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
